Differentially expressed genes (DEGs) for ma_plot function.

Source: R/deg_data2.R
deg_data2.Rd

Differentially expressed genes (DEGs) for ma_plot function.

Usage

data(deg_data2)

Format

Dataframe: include columns (Genes, baseMean, Log2FoldChange, Padj), rows (Genes).

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/MversusA/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(deg_data2)

# 3. View example data
deg_data2
